name: framework7
readme: [![Join the chat at https://gitter.im/nolimits4web/Framework7](https://badges.gitter.im/Join%20Chat.svg)](https://gitter.im/nolimits4web/Framework7) # Framework7 Full Featured Mobile HTML Framework For Building iOS & Android Apps ## Getting Started * [Getting Started Guide](https://framework7.io/docs/introduction.html) * [Installation Guide](http://framework7.io/docs/installation.html) * [App Layout](http://framework7.io/docs/app-layout.html) * [Initialize App](http://framework7.io/docs/init-app.html) ## Forum If you have questions about Framework7 or want to help others you are welcome to special forum at http://forum.framework7.io/ ## Docs Documentation available at http://framework7.io/docs/ ## Tutorials Tutorials available at http://framework7.io/tutorials/ ## Showcase Appstore apps made with Framework7: http://framework7.io/showcase/

scripts.postinstall: node -e "console.log('\u001b[35m\u001b[1mLove Framework7? Support project by donating or pledging on patreon:\u001b[22m\u001b[39m\n > \u001b[32mhttps://patreon.com/vladimirkharlampidi\u001b[0m\n')"
